      "para_id": "Q000951.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Enlil , king of all lands , his master , Ur-Namma , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , built his temple , and dug the Id-en-eren-nun canal , his canal of food offerings ."
    }
